Package: clinUtils
Type: Package
Title: General utility functions for analysis of clinical data
Version: 0.0.1.999
Date: 2021-04-19
Author: Laure Cougnaud and Michela Pasetto
Maintainer: Laure Cougnaud <laure.cougnaud@openanalytics.eu>
Description: 
 This package contains general utility functions to facilitate the import, 
 the reporting and analysis of clinical data.
 Example datasets in CDISC SDTM and ADaM format, containing a subset of patients/domain
 from the CDISC Pilot 01 study are also available as R datasets to demonstrate
 the package functionalities.
